向华盛顿鞠躬
Bow down to Washington

346
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:56,570
穿金戴银者威风凛凛
Mighty are the men who wear the purple and the gold

347
00:22:57,050 --> 00:22:59,840
我们高兴地欢迎他们加入胜利者的行列
Joyfully we welcome them within the victor's fold

348
00:22:59,940 --> 00:23:03,120
我们将把自己的名字刻在名人堂里
We will carve our names in the Hall of Fame

349
00:23:03,260 --> 00:23:06,670
为了保留我们奉献的记忆
To preserve the memory of our devotion

350
00:23:06,710 --> 00:23:10,180
所以，上天保佑华盛顿的敌人
So, heaven help the foes of Washington

351
00:23:10,310 --> 00:23:13,560
他们在强大的华盛顿脚下瑟瑟发抖
They're trembling at the feet of mighty Washington

352
00:23:13,660 --> 00:23:17,200
我们的小伙子在那里敲钟，他们的战斗血性出类拔萃
Our boys are there with bells, Their fighting blood excels

353
00:23:17,220 --> 00:23:20,440
把他们推过界线比通过....
It's harder to push them over the lines than pass...

354
00:23:37,440 --> 00:23:38,840
－嘿　－嗨
- Hey. - Hi.

355
00:23:39,140 --> 00:23:40,240
你...
You, uh...

356
00:23:40,620 --> 00:23:41,980
你想去赛艇上坐坐吗？
You wanna go for a boat ride?

357
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:43,280
现在？
Now?

358
00:23:44,340 --> 00:23:45,340
是啊
Yeah.

359
00:23:46,250 --> 00:23:47,280
好吧
Yeah, okay.

360
00:23:48,450 --> 00:23:51,060
入水，推进
Catch, drive,

361
00:23:51,120 --> 00:23:53,100
完成，归位
finish, recovery.

362
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:55,950
在重来一遍之前，你必须做完所有四个步骤
You gotta do all four before you can start again.

363
00:23:57,760 --> 00:23:59,450
好多了，下一步你要翻桨了
That's better. You gotta feather next.

364
00:23:59,770 --> 00:24:01,600
翻桨？什么是翻桨？
Feathering? What's feather?

365
00:24:03,200 --> 00:24:04,200
看这里
Here, look.

366
00:24:06,390 --> 00:24:07,930
你滚动你的手腕
You roll your wrists

367
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:09,480
转动艇桨
to spin the oar.

368
00:24:12,600 --> 00:24:14,060
－看到了吗？－嗯
- You see? - Mm.

369
00:24:16,010 --> 00:24:17,340
现在，再试一次
Now, try again.

370
00:24:21,520 --> 00:24:23,330
你是天生的
You're a natural.

371
00:24:23,470 --> 00:24:26,200
我以为你说要带我坐着艇兜风去
I thought you said you were gonna take me on a boat ride.

372
00:24:26,290 --> 00:24:27,920
好吧，坐过去点
All right, scooch over.

373
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:36,930
好的
All right.

374
00:24:37,670 --> 00:24:39,480
你喜欢吗？划艇？
Do you like it? Rowing?

375
00:24:40,700 --> 00:24:41,900
还行
Well,

376
00:24:42,690 --> 00:24:44,290
得到一份工作
gettin' a job out of it.

377
00:24:45,170 --> 00:24:47,240
还有一个房间，所以，我猜
And a room. So, I guess.

378
00:24:48,450 --> 00:24:50,030
