－他们输了　－他们今年更好
- And they lost. - They're better this year.

943
00:58:37,070 --> 00:58:38,370
如果不知道他们的年龄
If you didn't know their ages,

944
00:58:38,490 --> 00:58:40,160
不知道他们划了多久
you didn't know how long they've been rowing,

945
00:58:40,530 --> 00:58:42,030
假设你第一次看到这两艘艇...
you're looking at both boats for the first time...

946
00:58:42,110 --> 00:58:44,210
后院的计时赛不算
A time trial in the backyard does not count.

947
00:58:44,310 --> 00:58:45,700
这和正规赛场是两码事
That is not the same thing as a race.

948
00:58:45,780 --> 00:58:47,120
看看比赛时间
Look at the competition times.

949
00:58:47,140 --> 00:58:48,640
没那么容易
It's not that easy.

950
00:58:49,240 --> 00:58:50,610
拜托，你知道的
Come on, you know that.

951
00:58:50,660 --> 00:58:51,620
是的，是的
Yes. Yes.

952
00:58:52,890 --> 00:58:53,970
是的，我知道
Yes, I know.

953
00:58:54,010 --> 00:58:55,840
你表现得就像校队是群废物一样
You're acting like the varsity boat is scrappin'.

954
00:58:55,890 --> 00:58:58,130
要知道，那艘艇也没有输过比赛
You know that boat hasn't lost a race either.

955
00:58:58,340 --> 00:58:59,640
就在不久前
And it wasn't that long ago

956
00:58:59,680 --> 00:59:01,320
你还在期待初级队
you were just hopin' the JV boat

957
00:59:01,340 --> 00:59:03,180
能在不沉没的情况下坚持到终点
was gonna make it to the finish line without sinking.

958
00:59:03,210 --> 00:59:04,710
现在，艾尔
Now, Al,

959
00:59:04,740 --> 00:59:06,530
现在你却说要把我们所有的筹码都押在他们身上
now you're talkin' about putting all our chips on 'em.

960
00:59:06,570 --> 00:59:08,500
你认为校队能在柏林拿奖吗？
Do you think varsity could medal in Berlin?

961
00:59:08,530 --> 00:59:09,990
我们不是在谈论奖牌
We're not talkin' about a medal.

962
00:59:10,010 --> 00:59:11,450
我们说的是去那里的机会
We're talkin' about a shot at gettin' there.

963
00:59:11,490 --> 00:59:13,230
就算他们到了那？
If they got there?

964
00:59:15,840 --> 00:59:17,170
我不知道
I don't know.

965
00:59:27,820 --> 00:59:29,690
我们今年需要一场胜利，艾尔
We need a win this year, Al.

966
00:59:30,810 --> 00:59:33,380
给我们付钱的人，他们需要一场胜利
The people who pay us, they need a win.

967
00:59:33,980 --> 00:59:36,320
你派一艇孩子过去
You send a boat full of kids down there

968
00:59:36,340 --> 00:59:37,750
他们就会被绊倒
and they trip up,

969
00:59:38,070 --> 00:59:39,740
你就等着
you're sticking your neck way out there.

970
00:59:39,820 --> 00:59:42,690
引颈就戮吧，我也是
Makes it a real easy target. And mine, too.

971
00:59:43,500 --> 00:59:44,970
我需要这份工作
I need this job.

972
01:00:01,450 --> 01:00:02,910
你怎么看，乔治？
What do you think, George?

973
01:00:03,810 --> 01:00:04,840
嗯
Hmm.

974
01:00:09,830 --> 01:00:11,390
你在艇上那会
When you were in a boat,

975
01:00:11,790 --> 01:00:15,120
你的划艇技术这里无人能及
you rowed like no one else that's ever come through here.

976
01:00:15,140 --> 01:00:16,580
我记得我看着你
I remember watching you,

977
01:00:16,660 --> 01:00:18,860
真想知道我的船到底能跑多快
wondering how fast one of my shells could go

978
01:00:18,890 --> 01:00:20,920
如果里面有8个和你一样的人
if there were eight just like you in it.

979
01:00:22,340 --> 01:00:24,080
那群孩子
That bunch of kids

980
01:00:25,130 --> 01:00:27,730
可能是最接近我这想法的了
might be as close to that as I'll ever get.

981
01:00:30,030 --> 01:00:33,330
如果我把他们派出去，他们还没准备好呢？
And if I send them out there and they aren't ready?

982
01:00:33,360 --> 01:00:34,990
那就像汤姆说的那样
Then it's like Tom said.

983
01:00:35,370 --> 01:00:37,540
斧头很可能会落下
The axe will likely fall,

984
01:00:37,770 --> 01:00:39,030
砍得脖子疼
and fall hard.

985
01:00:39,550 --> 01:00:41,510
现在你的口气开始像我妻子了
Now you're starting to sound like my wife.

986
01:00:41,970 --> 01:00:44,310
海泽尔是个聪明的女人
Well, Hazel's a smart woman.

987
01:00:44,340 --> 01:00:46,440
我就当你在夸我
I'll take that as a compliment.

988
01:00:54,510 --> 01:00:56,480
大家早上好
Good morning, everybody.

989
01:00:57,450 --> 01:00:58,660
谢谢
Thank you.

990
01:01:00,220 --> 01:01:03,060
众所周知，波基普西帆艇赛
Now, as we all know, uh, the Poughkeepsie Regatta

991
01:01:03,080 --> 01:01:05,860
一直是本赛季最重要的比赛
is always the most important race of the season.

992
01:01:08,800 --> 01:01:11,110
今年，它的意义更加重大
This year, there's even more riding on it,

993
01:01:11,140 --> 01:01:14,650
因为获胜者将获得奥运会的参赛资格
because the winner will qualify for an Olympic spot.

994
01:01:14,680 --> 01:01:16,710
好
Yes!

995
01:01:20,840 --> 01:01:23,910
它也是华盛顿大学已近20年
It's also a race that the University of Washington

996
01:01:24,610 --> 01:01:27,480
未尝胜绩的一个赛事
has not won in almost two decades,

997
01:01:27,550 --> 01:01:30,110
但是...
but... but...

998
01:01:31,740 --> 01:01:34,580
我们今年有一艘艇
we have a boat this year

999
01:01:34,720 --> 01:01:36,860
我相信他们可以改变这一切
that I believe could change all that.

1000
01:01:38,850 --> 01:01:41,920
这艘艇不仅能在波基普西夺冠
A boat that could not only win at Poughkeepsie,

1001
01:01:42,600 --> 01:01:43,730
而且
but

1002
01:01:44,090 --> 01:01:46,260
有足够的实力在柏林一展身手
is strong enough to have a real shot in Berlin.

1003
01:02:03,270 --> 01:02:04,470
还有...
And, uh...

1004
01:02:06,890 --> 01:02:08,990
那艘艇就是我们的初级艇
that boat is our junior boat.

1005
01:02:12,170 --> 01:02:13,660
是的，你们都听到了
Yeah, you heard me.

1006
01:02:15,650 --> 01:02:17,880
听着，我知道这不合常理
Listen, I understand that that's unorthodox.

1007
01:02:17,930 --> 01:02:20,270
－不合常理？简直是疯了　－我正在尽我所能...
- Unorthodox? It's insane. - I'm doing everything I can...

1008
01:02:20,300 --> 01:02:21,460
你不能这么做
You can't do that.

1009
01:02:21,490 --> 01:02:22,870
我们团队和华盛顿大学的
in the best interests of our team

1010
01:02:22,900 --> 01:02:24,370
最佳利益
and the University of Washington.

1011
01:02:24,400 --> 01:02:26,000
谢谢
Thank you.

1012
01:02:32,590 --> 01:02:33,900
这简直是胡扯！
This is bullshit!

1013
01:02:37,620 --> 01:02:39,050
你疯了吗？
Have you lost your mind?

1014
01:02:39,210 --> 01:02:40,360
那些花了四年时间
What about those boys who spent

1015
01:02:40,390 --> 01:02:41,890
在这上面的孩子怎么办？
the last four years working for this?

1016
01:02:41,990 --> 01:02:43,430
我的工作就是派最好的艇去参赛，本
My job is to put the best boat in the water, Ben.

1017
01:02:43,450 --> 01:02:45,320
你的工作？我付的钱
Your job? I pay for your job.

1018
01:02:45,760 --> 01:02:46,870
没有我支持，你认为
Without the boosters, where do you think

1019
01:02:46,890 --> 01:02:48,160
你们买艇的钱是从哪里来的？
the money for your boats comes from, huh?

1020
01:02:48,180 --> 01:02:49,320
你那该死的薪水哪里来
For your goddamn salary?

1021
01:02:49,340 --> 01:02:50,630
让我做我的工作怎么样？
How about you let me do my job?

1022
01:02:50,660 --> 01:02:51,860
让我们安定下来
Let's just settle down

1023
01:02:51,990 --> 01:02:53,760
冷静地谈谈，来吧
and talk about this calmly. Come on.

1024
01:02:53,780 --> 01:02:55,240
没什么好谈的，杰伊
There's nothin' to talk about, Jay.

1025
01:02:55,300 --> 01:02:56,770
我的团队，我做主
My team, my decision.

1026
01:02:57,010 --> 01:02:58,640
那就不再是你的团队了
Then it's not your team anymore.

1027
01:02:58,830 --> 01:03:00,330
我会让你屁股挪窝
I'll make sure your ass is fired

1028
01:03:00,360 --> 01:03:01,570
在火车开往波基普西之前
before the train leaves for Poughkeepsie.

1029
01:03:01,610 --> 01:03:03,050
－本，我们不会搞到...　－好吧
- Ben, we're not gonna get... - All right.

1030
01:03:03,100 --> 01:03:04,670
博勒斯和你一样能干
Bolles is just as capable as you.

1031
01:03:04,800 --> 01:03:05,730
甚至更好
Better even.

1032
01:03:05,800 --> 01:03:07,370
我会和艾尔一样选择
I'd do the same as Al.

1033
01:03:16,090 --> 01:03:17,830
我希望你知道自己在做什么
I hope you know what you're doing.

1034
01:03:19,680 --> 01:03:20,950
本
Ben!

1035
01:03:26,950 --> 01:03:28,220
我知道吗？
Do I?

1036
01:03:30,040 --> 01:03:31,310
你当然知道
Sure you do.

1037
01:03:33,950 --> 01:03:35,560
真不敢相信你要去参加奥运会
I can't believe you're going to the Olympics.

1038
01:03:35,750 --> 01:03:37,180
我们得先打败其他学校
We gotta beat those other schools first,

1039
01:03:37,200 --> 01:03:39,860
但教练说，我们的机会和其他队一样多
but Coach says we have as good a shot as anybody.

1040
01:03:40,970 --> 01:03:43,350
你不准和那些纽约女孩调情
You can't flirt with any of those New York girls.

1041
01:03:56,500 --> 01:03:57,760
怎么了？
What's wrong?

1042
01:03:59,270 --> 01:04:00,570
马上回来
Be back in a second.

1043
01:04:05,590 --> 01:04:06,830
乔？
Joe?

1044
01:04:39,330 --> 01:04:41,340
在报纸上看到你的照片了
Saw your picture in the paper.

1045
01:04:42,090 --> 01:04:43,900
小哈利把它剪了下来
Harry Junior clipped it out.

1046
01:04:46,160 --> 01:04:47,920
你们什么时候从加州回来的？
When did you get back from California?

1047
01:04:47,950 --> 01:04:49,350
好几年了
Couple of years.

1048
01:04:49,860 --> 01:04:52,260
那里的情况也没好到哪里去
You know, things weren't much better down there.

1049
01:04:53,750 --> 01:04:55,780
这么说，你一直都在这里？
So, you've been here all that time?

1050
01:04:55,880 --> 01:04:57,070
就在前面一点点远
Down the road a bit.

1051
01:04:57,220 --> 01:04:58,590
你打算告诉我吗？
Were you ever gonna tell me?

1052
01:04:58,810 --> 01:05:00,320
你做得很好
You're doin' all right.

1053
01:05:00,580 --> 01:05:01,780
你离开的时候，我才14岁
I was 14 when you left.

1054
01:05:01,800 --> 01:05:04,040
我在那个年纪就上战场了
I went to war when I was that age.

1055
01:05:09,760 --> 01:05:11,320
那么，你在想什么，乔？
So, what do you wanna do, Joe?

1056
01:05:12,490 --> 01:05:13,720
啊？
Huh?

1057
01:05:14,010 --> 01:05:15,040
想搬回家吗？
Move home?

1058
01:05:15,290 --> 01:05:16,620
我是说，我需要人帮忙
I mean, I could use the help.

1059
01:05:16,760 --> 01:05:18,260
这样吧，我每天付你一美元
Tell you what, I'll pay you a dollar a day

1060
01:05:18,360 --> 01:05:20,390
如果你还记得如何砍树的话
if you still remember how to cut a tree.

1061
01:05:24,300 --> 01:05:27,100
或者，你宁愿继续划你的艇
Or maybe you'd rather just keep rowing your boat.

1062
01:05:30,200 --> 01:05:31,970
你不欠我什么，乔
You don't owe me a thing, Joe.

1063
01:05:33,480 --> 01:05:34,570
我也不欠你的
I don't owe you.

1064
01:05:35,410 --> 01:05:37,020
你做得很好
You're doing just fine.

1065
01:05:39,880 --> 01:05:41,610
我会转达问候的
I'll pass on regards.

1066
01:05:56,300 --> 01:05:57,500
对不起
I'm sorry.

1067
01:05:59,770 --> 01:06:01,370
这结果是最好的
Works out for the best.

1068
01:06:05,220 --> 01:06:07,580
是的，但这并不意味着就没事了
Yeah, but that doesn't make it okay.

1069
01:06:08,800 --> 01:06:10,140
也许吧
Maybe.

1070
01:06:17,540 --> 01:06:19,040
我得走了
I gotta go.

1071
01:07:06,240 --> 01:07:07,640
你应该来睡一觉
You should come get some sleep

1072
01:07:07,670 --> 01:07:09,770
在太阳升起之前
before the sun rises over that.

1073
01:07:10,400 --> 01:07:12,110
我很快就过去
I'll be in there soon.

1074
01:07:17,350 --> 01:07:19,880
我真喜欢这样的景色
I sure love that view.

1075
01:07:22,950 --> 01:07:24,160
我知道
I know.

1076
01:07:25,560 --> 01:07:29,330
我只是希望我能像以前那样享受它
I just wish I could enjoy it the way I used to.

1077
01:07:30,700 --> 01:07:31,760
为什么不能
Why don't you

1078
01:07:32,400 --> 01:07:35,300
要来看看有没有其他风景可以欣赏吗？
come see if there's another view you can enjoy?

1079
01:07:45,580 --> 01:07:46,640
好吧
Okay.

1080
01:08:30,350 --> 01:08:31,520
谢谢
Thank you.

1081
01:08:32,740 --> 01:08:35,130
我们会成为世界上最快的艇员
We're gonna be the fastest crew the world has ever seen.

1082
01:08:35,730 --> 01:08:37,070
把冠军带回家，艾尔
Bring home the championship, Al!

1083
01:08:37,160 --> 01:08:39,200
－还有一枚金牌　－我们会努力的
- And a gold medal! - We'll try.

1084
01:08:40,330 --> 01:08:41,330
哦，天哪
Oh, boy.

1085
01:08:41,840 --> 01:08:44,280
我们可能想赢得比赛，对吧？
We might wanna try and win this thing, huh?

1086
01:08:44,940 --> 01:08:46,240
没有压力
No pressure.

1087
01:08:47,550 --> 01:08:49,240
－祝你们好运　－把奖牌带回家，孩子们
- Good luck! - Bring it home, boys!

1088
01:08:49,510 --> 01:08:51,440
我会通过收音机收听
I'll be listening on the radio.

1089
01:08:52,680 --> 01:08:54,740
如果他们采访你，跟我问个好
Say hello if they interview you.

1090
01:08:56,720 --> 01:08:58,250
现在也许是个好机会
This might be a good time to tell you

1091
01:08:58,280 --> 01:08:59,790
告诉你我爱上你了，乔
that I'm in love with you, Joe.

1092
01:09:01,040 --> 01:09:03,870
好，我得走了
All right. I gotta go.

1093
01:09:13,600 --> 01:09:15,770
嘿！
Hey! Hey!

1094
01:09:16,760 --> 01:09:18,340
是的，她看着我
Yeah, she looked at me.

1095
01:09:57,440 --> 01:09:58,640
兰茨
Rantz!

1096
01:10:32,380 --> 01:10:33,950
我破产了，谁给我一便士
I'm busted. Someone give me a penny.

1097
01:10:34,080 --> 01:10:35,080
幸运，我会让你看看的
Lucky, I'll let you watch.

1098
01:10:35,210 --> 01:10:36,300
嘿，乔，把你的夹克给我
Hey, Joe, give me your jacket.

1099
01:10:36,450 --> 01:10:37,850
这样我有一半押注的钱了
That'll get me halfway to ante.

1100
01:10:38,040 --> 01:10:39,350
乔，别走
Joe, stick around.

1101
01:10:39,480 --> 01:10:41,220
嘿，别走啊，流浪汉乔
Hey, don't run away, Hobo Joe.

1102
01:10:44,300 --> 01:10:45,570
他开玩笑的
He's playin'.

1103
01:10:46,390 --> 01:10:48,120
他开玩笑的，他开玩笑的
He's playin'. He's playin'.

1104
01:10:48,250 --> 01:10:49,480
他开玩笑的
He's playin'.

1105
01:10:54,160 --> 01:10:56,430
－天啊，查克　－开个玩笑而已
- Jesus, Chuck. - Was just jokin'.

1106
01:10:57,460 --> 01:10:59,260
好吧，你的笑话太烂了
Yeah, well, your jokes are lousy.

1107
01:11:38,600 --> 01:11:40,200
我没有别的意思
I didn't mean anything by it.

1108
01:11:42,250 --> 01:11:45,450
事实是，我老爸几年前就破产了，所以...
Truth is, my old man went bust years ago, so...

1109
01:11:46,060 --> 01:11:48,930
我穿的新衣服，都是从伍尔沃斯超市顺来的
Any new clothes I wear, I swipe from Woolworth's.

1110
01:11:51,190 --> 01:11:52,450
无所谓
Doesn't matter.

1111
01:11:54,370 --> 01:11:56,140
我只是说，我们并没有什么不同
Just sayin' we're not different.

1112
01:11:56,630 --> 01:11:57,830
你和我
You and me.

1113
01:11:59,920 --> 01:12:01,720
只不过你不是小偷
Except you're not a thief.

1114
01:12:18,220 --> 01:12:20,020
一，停桨
One! Way-nuff!

1115
01:12:20,320 --> 01:12:21,520
放下
Drop it.

1116
01:12:22,350 --> 01:12:24,950
再来一次！节奏再快一点
Again! Need to get sharper.

1117
01:12:25,100 --> 01:12:26,130
来吧
Come on.

1118
01:12:26,260 --> 01:12:28,170
你们不同步，跟着休姆
You guys are out of sync. Find Hume.

1119
01:12:28,300 --> 01:12:29,440
跟着休姆的节奏
Take it off Hume.

1120
01:12:29,570 --> 01:12:31,170
像个团队，伙计们
Look like a team, fellas.

1121
01:12:31,330 --> 01:12:32,530
同步
As one.

1122
01:12:32,550 --> 01:12:33,710
你们不同步
You're out of sync.

1123
01:12:33,830 --> 01:12:36,080
好吧，不，停桨
Okay, no, no. Way-nuff.

1124
01:12:37,230 --> 01:12:39,190
我们要去哪里？嘿，乔，你和我们在一起吗？
Where are we off? Hey, Joe, you with us?

1125
01:12:39,270 --> 01:12:40,910
－我　－对，锁定唐的节奏
- Me? - Yeah, lock in on Don.

1126
01:12:40,930 --> 01:12:42,650
你在说什么？我不是问题所在
What are you talkin' about? I'm not the problem.

1127
01:12:44,220 --> 01:12:45,390
再来一次
Go again.

1128
